d&rsquo;esquiver les balles, puisqu&rsquo;on ne les voit plus bouger une fois en mouvement. Le mieux que l&rsquo;on peut faire est de prendre des mesures défensives, pour se rendre plus difficile &agrave; toucher (cf. Se mettre &agrave; couvert, page 100).</p>\n<p>L&rsquo;Esquive progresse avec l&rsquo;expérience, comme n&rsquo;importe quelle compétence.</p>\n<h2>Compétence opposée / Niveau de difficulté :</h2>\n<p>Servant essentiellement lors de tests opposés en combat, l&rsquo;esquive n&rsquo;a pas de difficulté fixe.</p>\n<p><strong> Note :</strong> En tant que compétence de combat, le redoublement est impossible.</p>","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":"","keeper":""},"base":25,"bonusDice":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":25,"attributes":{},"properties":{"fighting":true,"firearm":false,"combat":true,"special":false},"flags":{},"eras":{}},"ownership":{"default":0,"cyefC9RG9awp41sM":3,"MB3cBb00LglcX37K":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"CoC7","systemVersion":"0.10.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676310771066,"modifiedTime":1686954603845,"lastModifiedBy":"MB3cBb00LglcX37K"}}],"effects":[],"sort":500000,"ownership":{"default":0,"MB3cBb00LglcX37K":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"CoC7","systemVersion":"0.10.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686954592518,"modifiedTime":1687118809898,"lastModifiedBy":"MB3cBb00LglcX37K"},"_id":"UVEbE20LcWqNKMc0"},{"name":"Jumoke*","type":"npc","folder":"TngPdKtVsYpM3BVp","system":{"characteristics":{"str":{"value":40,"tempValue":null,"short":"CHARAC.STR","label":"CHARAC.Strength","formula":null,"bonusDice":0},"con":{"value":50,"tempValue":null,"short":"CHARAC.CON","label":"CHARAC.Constitution","formula":null,"bonusDice":0},"siz":{"value":60,"tempValue":null,"short":"CHARAC.SIZ","label":"CHARAC.Size","formula":null,"bonusDice":0},"dex":{"value":50,"tempValue":null,"short":"CHARAC.DEX","label":"CHARAC.Dexterity","formula":null,"bonusDice":0