i mangeait une soupe seul à la table d’à côté, tendit l’oreille en l’entendant mentionner l’emplacement de la tombe KV62. Walsh expliqua tout à ses amis, décrivant avec force détails le couloir et l’existence d’au moins trois chambres sacrées, précisant que la sépulture était non seulement celle du pharaon infirme mais aussi de sa famille du côté paternel. Il se souvient parfaitement que <strong>Carter</strong> nota tout ceci dans un carnet, sur la couverture duquel il avait écrit « Toutânkhamon ». Andrew Walsh est un humble égyptologue rongé par la jalousie.</p>"}}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","prototypeToken":{"name":"Andrew Walsh","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"texture":{"src":"modules/adc-farce-macabre/assets/characters/npc/individu_lambda.webp","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":"attribs.hp"},"bar2":{"attribute":"attribs.san"},"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"color":null,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"attenuation":0.5,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"type":null,"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1}},"sight":{"enabled":false,"range":null,"angle":360,"visionMode":"basic","color":null,"attenuation":0.1,"brightness":0,"saturation":0,"contrast":0},"detectionModes":[],"flags":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"type":"skill","name":"Combat rapproché (Corps à corps)","system":{"skillName":"Corps à corps","specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":"","keeper":""},"base":25,"bonusDice":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":25,"attributes":{},"properties":{"special":true,"fighting":true,"firearm":false,"combat":true},"flags":{}},"img":"systems/CoC7/assets/icons/skills.svg","_id":"JsA56TwYFJEttP49","eff