 possède des caravanes de chameaux qui effectuent la traversée du désert. Au marché de Souq al-Gamaal, il les entraîne et les loue aux touristes. Il prend les paris des courses et connaît le <strong>prince Fouad</strong>, un grand passionné. Il lui manque un doigt à chaque main, mangés par les chameaux. Quiconque rend hommage au <strong>prince</strong> en sa présence obtient un dé bonus à ses tests de <strong>Crédit</strong> avec lui.</p>"}}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","prototypeToken":{"name":"Funsani Musleh","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"texture":{"src":"modules/adc-farce-macabre/assets/characters/npc/individu_lambda.webp","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":"attribs.hp"},"bar2":{"attribute":"attribs.san"},"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"color":null,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"attenuation":0.5,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"type":null,"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1}},"sight":{"enabled":false,"range":null,"angle":360,"visionMode":"basic","color":null,"attenuation":0.1,"brightness":0,"saturation":0,"contrast":0},"detectionModes":[],"flags":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"type":"skill","name":"Combat rapproché (Corps à corps)","system":{"skillName":"Corps à corps","specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":"","keeper":""},"base":25,"bonusDice":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":25,"attributes":{},"properties":{"special":true,"fighting":true,"firearm":false,"combat":true},"flags":{}},"img":"systems/CoC7/assets/icons/skills.svg","_id":"JsA56TwYFJEttP49","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"MB3cBb00LglcX37K":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"CoC7","systemVersion":"0.10.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1688333596983,"modifiedTime":1688333596983,"lastModifiedBy":"MB3cBb00LglcX37K"}},{"name":"Corps à corps","type":"weapon","system":{"description":{"value":"","chat":"","special":"","keeper":""},"wpnType":"","skill":{"main":{"name":"Combat rapproché (Corps à corps)","id":"JsA56TwYFJEttP49"},"alternativ":{"name":"","id":""},"id":null},"range":{"normal":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":"1D3-1"},"long":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""},"extreme":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""}},"usesPerRound":{"normal":1,"max":null,"burst":null},"bullets":null,"ammo":0,"malfunction":null,"blastRadius":null,"properties":{"shotgun":false,"rngd":false,"melee":true,"ahdb":false,"addb":false},"price":{}},"img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","_id":"Iko9qZXztxgPklLL","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"MB3cBb00LglcX37K":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"CoC7","systemVersion":"0.10.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1688333596984,"modifiedTime":1688333597033,"lastModifiedBy":"MB3cBb00LglcX37K"}},{"name":"Esquive","type":"skill","system":{"skillName":"Esquive","specialization":"","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":"","keeper":""},"base":null,"bonusDice":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":22,"attributes":{},"properties":{"special":false,"rarity":false,"push":false,"combat":false},"flags":{}},"img":"systems/CoC7/assets/icons/skills.svg","_id":"pTKfuLBVWkAU7aMQ","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"MB3cBb00LglcX37K":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"CoC7","systemVersion":"0.10.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1688333596984,"modifiedTime":1688333596984,"lastModifiedBy":"MB3cBb00LglcX37K"}},{"_id":"3MNdOuqoE8kJi9TR","name":"Baratin","type":"skill","img":"modules/coc7-module-fr-toc-full/icones/competences-fasttalk.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_se2twz2lkhc","path":"Compétences","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.CoC7-compendiums-fr.competences.GH4LKEwyTE2izw8u"}},"system":{"skillName":"Baratin","specialization":"","description":{"value":"<p>Le Baratin sert &agrave; bluffer, emberlificoter&nbsp;et tromper par le discours. Il permet par&nbsp;exemple d&rsquo;amadouer un videur pour qu&rsquo;il vous laisse entrer dans un club, de faire signer un contrat &agrave; un pigeon sans qu&rsquo;il l&rsquo;ait lu, d&rsquo;apitoyer un policier pour qu&rsquo;il ne vous mette pas d&rsquo;amende, et ainsi de suite. Le test est opposé &agrave; la Psychologie ou au Baratin de la cible. Après quelques instants, elle réalise qu&rsquo;elle s&rsquo;est fait avoir. Mieux vaut ne plus &ecirc;tre dans les parages. L&rsquo;effet est toujours temporaire, mais il durera un peu plus longtemps en cas de réussite majeure ou extr&ecirc;me.</p>\n<p>Cette compétence sert aussi &agrave; marchander pour obtenir un rabais auprès d&rsquo;un vendeur. En cas de succès, il pense faire une bonne affaire. Toutefois, si l&rsquo;investigateur revient quelques jours plus tard, le commer&ccedil;ant risque de refuser de marchander avec lui, voire augmenter d&rsquo;office ses prix, pour compenser la perte de sa dernière visite !</p>\n<h2>Compétence opposée / Niveau de difficulté :</h2>\n<p>Consultez Fixer la difficulté des compétences sociales, page 82.</p>\n<h2>Comment redoubler ?</h2>\n<p>S&rsquo;approcher de très près de sa cible ; user d&rsquo;un vocabulaire recherché dans le but de confondre la cible. Rappelez-vous qu&rsquo;il s&rsquo;agit d&rsquo;un Baratin. Si un investigateur opte pour une autre approche en cours de route, le gardien peut demander un test d&rsquo;une compétence différente. S&rsquo;il profère des menaces, ce sera Intimidation. S&rsquo;il encha&icirc;ne sur une longue discussion, cela peut devenir de la Persuasion. Passer de l&rsquo;un &agrave; l&rsquo;autre pour obtenir une deuxième chance constitue un redoublement.</p>\n<h2>Conséquences d&rsquo;un redoublement raté ?</h2>\n<p>La cible est outrée par la manoeuvre, peut-&ecirc;tre au point de devenir violente ou de porter plainte. Si un investigateur dément rate un redoublement, il peut se mettre &agrave; vomir des insanités sans aucune retenue.</p>","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":"","keeper":""},"base":25,"bonusDice":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":25,"attributes":{},"properties":{"special":false,"push":true,"fighting":false,"firearm":false,"combat":false,"noadjustments":false},"flags":{},"eras":{}},"ownership":{"default":0,"cyefC9RG9awp41sM":3,"MB3cBb00LglcX37K":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"CoC7","systemVersion":"0.10.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676310771107,"modifiedTime":1688333596985,"lastModifiedBy":"MB3cBb00LglcX37K"}},{"name":"Charme ou Intimidation","type":"skill","system":{"skillName":"Charme ou Intimidation","specialization":"","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":"","keeper":""},"base":null,"bonusDice":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":20,"attributes":{},"properties":{"special":false,"rarity":false,"push":true,"combat":false},"flags":{}},"img":"systems/CoC7/assets/icons/skills.svg","_id":"6CSAWeM0x23JWyxy","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"MB3cBb00LglcX37K":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"CoC7","systemVersion":"0.10.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1688333596986,"modifiedTime":1688333596986,"lastModifiedBy":"MB3cBb00LglcX37K"}},{"_id":"QgqncCiJPQHLa707","name":"Crédit","type":"skill","img":"modules/coc7-module-fr-toc-full/icones/competences-creditrating.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_se2twz2lkhc","path":"Compétences","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.CoC7-compendiums-fr.competences.zyrOLKVlX9nZ6hHC"}},"system":{"