enir un prêt.</p>\n<h2>Conséquences d’un redoublement raté ?</h2>\n<p>L’usurier véreux perd patience et envoie ses gars vous donner une leçon ; le banquier appelle la police ; la pègre vous prête l’argent, mais c’est une manoeuvre pour vous faire crouler sous les dettes et exiger une faveur.</p>\n<p>Si un investigateur dément rate un redoublement, il peut perdre sa confiance dans le capitalisme et jeter littéralement son argent par les fenêtres. Voir aussi Dépenses courantes et Niveau de vie, page 84.</p>","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":"","keeper":""},"base":20,"bonusDice":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":20,"attributes":{},"properties":{"noxpgain":true,"push":true},"flags":{},"eras":{}},"ownership":{"default":0,"cyefC9RG9awp41sM":3,"MB3cBb00LglcX37K":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"CoC7","systemVersion":"0.10.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676310772187,"modifiedTime":1688333596986,"lastModifiedBy":"MB3cBb00LglcX37K"}},{"name":"Persuasion (Déblatérer des sottises sans intérêt)","type":"skill","system":{"skillName":"Persuasion (Déblatérer des sottises sans intérêt)","specialization":"","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":"","keeper":""},"base":null,"bonusDice":0,"adjustments":{"personal":null,"occupation":null,"archetype":null,"experience":null},"value":25,"attributes":{},"properties":{"special":false,"rarity":false,"push":true,"combat":false},"flags":{}},"img":"systems/CoC7/assets/icons/skills.svg","_id":"ohVu3PLlEF33lzhq","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"MB3cBb00LglcX37K":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"CoC7","systemVersion":"0.10.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1688333596987,"modifiedTime":1688333596987,"lastModifiedBy":"MB3cBb00LglcX37K"}},{"name":"Language (Anglais (Langue maternelle))","type":"skill","system":{"skillName":"Anglais (Langue maternelle)","specialization":"Lan